caption.body: Director Linda Brownlee profiles the Haitian-born, Brussels-based street dancer Olivier Chapusette and his passion for dance in this intimate portrait shot almost entirely on an interior stairwell.  See "Limber Notes: 'Olivier'" by Linda Brownlee, now playing, in the Video Arts gallery, pre-security, in the International Terminal. http://www.flysfo.com/museum/video-arts/limber-notes-%E2%80%9Colivier%E2%80%9D
